0.1.name: bainternet/sqlite-simple-store
0.1.description: Super lightweight Zero configuration sqlite-based key => value store with expiration time for PHP. Basically its a simple key value storage with and expireation field which will delete the value after it expires. Also since its heavily influenced by redis, some of redis useful functions were implemented.
